      "rawTextPreview": "INNOVATIVE STUDY CIRCLE\nwhere education meets life\nExcretory system\n\u25cf\nExcretory system is responsible for removal of waste\nproducts derived from organisms\nmetabolism. The excretory system purifies blood.\n\u25cf\nIt removes urea, uric acid, ammonia, excess water\nand salts\n\u25cf\nExcretory system consists of a pair of kidney, one\nurator arising from each kidney\nleading to to the urinary bladder and the opening\nof the urinary bladder called the urethra\n\u25cf\nNephron is the functional and structural unit of the\nki"
